        <abstract>
            <p>Comments on glaciers in North America.</p> 
<p>Asks if glacial periods have occurred alternately in the Northern and Southern Hemispheres. Relevant to his glacial discoveries in South America: "it would have been an immense relief to my mind if I could have assumed … this". CD wishes to discuss subject in new edition of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> [5th].</p> 
        </abstract>
